com.cyc.base.kbtool

Interface InspectorTool

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CycInspectorTool

    public interface InspectorTool
    Tools for examining individual CycObjects. To examine the relationship between different CycObjects, use the ComparisonTool.
    See Also:
    ComparisonTool
